/**
 * ============================================================
 * KENFOLIOS LIVE INTERACTION GROUP WORKER
 * ============================================================
 *
 * This Cloudflare Worker manages the KenFolios
 * Live Interaction Group on Telegram.
 *
 * Features
 * --------
 *
 * • Automatically approves join requests for
 *   eligible members.
 *
 * • Removes members who are no longer eligible
 *   to remain in the Live Interaction Group.
 *
 * • Posts one community reminder every
 *   15 minutes.
 *
 * • Uses a sequential reminder library
 *   containing 144 templates.
 *
 * Cloudflare Cron
 * ---------------
 *
 * Configure ONE Cron Trigger in Cloudflare
 * to run every 15 minutes.
 *
 * Environment Variables
 * ---------------------
 *
 * TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN
 * TELEGRAM_LIVE_CHAT_ID
 * TELEGRAM_ANNOUNCEMENT_CHAT_ID
 *
 * ============================================================
 */


/* ============================================================
   CONFIGURATION
============================================================ */


/* ------------------------------------------------------------
   Telegram Groups
------------------------------------------------------------ */

